# Valid scholarly DOI links that currently reject automated CI checks.
# Manual-check list (paste each URL into a browser at each major review):
#   - https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.1317504111
#       Fischhoff & Davis (2014), PNAS              → flow/10_communication.ipynb
#   - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1745-6584.2005.00052.x
#       Anderson (2005), Ground Water               → transport/2_perceptual_model.ipynb
#   - https://doi.org/10.1029/92WR00607
#       Gelhar, Welty & Rehfeldt (1992), WRR        → transport/2_perceptual_model.ipynb
#       NOTE: redirects to agupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com which bot-blocks
#       (HTTP 403 / Cloudflare challenge) — DOI is canonical & verified.
#       If browser is blocked, verify via Google Scholar:
#       https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=10.1029%2F92WR00607
#   - https://doi.org/10.1146/annurev-statistics-010814-020148
#       Spiegelhalter (2017), Annu. Rev. Statistics → flow/10_communication.ipynb
^https://doi\.org/10\.1073/pnas\.1317504111$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1111/j\.1745-6584\.2005\.00052\.x$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1029/92WR00607$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1146/annurev-statistics-010814-020148$
